      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "The cmdlet returns an array of objects each of type <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Microsoft.PowerShell.xDscDiagnostics.GroupedEvents<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>.",
      "pos": [
        15205,
