      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>SequenceID<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>: Specifies the incremental number assigned to the DSC operation based on time.",
      "pos": [
        15445,
        15538
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "For example, the last executed operation would have SequenceID as 1, the second to last DSC operation would have SequenceID of 2, and so on.",
      "pos": [
        15539,
        15679
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "This number is another identifier for each object in the returned array.",
